<section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-20" style="background: #F5F2EC;">
  <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;" class="reveal-hidden">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
      <!-- Photo -->
      <div class="shrink-0" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%; overflow: hidden; border: 3px solid rgba(196,120,58,0.25);">
        {%- if section.settings.founder_image != blank -%}
          <img src="{{ section.settings.founder_image | image_url: width: 400 }}" alt="Gurkamal, Founder" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
        {%- else -%}
          <div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; background: #1C2E23; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
            <span class="font-heading text-36" style="color: #C4783A;">G</span>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono-spec text-11 uppercase mb-3" style="color: #C4783A; letter-spacing: 0.15em;">From the Founder</p>
        <p class="font-display text-22 italic mb-4" style="color: #1C2E23; line-height: 1.4;">
          &ldquo;I built Origin because the supplement industry ignored us. Generic probiotics were never tested on people who look like us, eat like us, or carry the microbiome we carry.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <p class="font-heading text-14 font-light mb-4" style="color: #4A5550; line-height: 1.7;">
          When I discovered that ethnicity determines your gut bacteria more than diet, age, sex, or medical history — I knew something was broken. Every probiotic on the shelf was formulated for a population that doesn't include most of us. That's why I started BaseCode Health and built Origin from the ground up.
        </p>
        <p class="font-heading text-14 font-medium" style="color: #1C2E23;">
          — Gurkamal, Founder · BaseCode Health
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Product Founder",
  "class": "product-founder-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "founder_image",
      "label": "Founder Photo"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
